Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:38.26,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:46.69,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}燃えて抱きしめてみるのは罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:53.65,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:59.24,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}嘆いても夢は唄わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:05.25,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所で叫んだよ「答えは誰が持ってるの？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:09.71,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}俯いたままじゃ気付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:15.97,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君の瞳の中　未来を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.22,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}もしも奇跡が今を指すなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.93,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}にじむ涙ぬぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.48,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}前を向いて歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:31.32,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}私を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:37.03,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}こんな苦しさで何も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:42.12,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:50.13,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}燃えて彼方へ　情熱は罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:57.38,OP_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:38.26,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:46.69,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}想用熊熊燃燒的胸懷抱緊你 這不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:53.65,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:59.24,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}自哀之人怎能唱出夢想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:05.25,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}站在原地嘶吼“到底誰能給我答案？”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:09.71,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}抬起頭來才能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:15.97,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}你的瞳孔中有著我尋覓已久的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.22,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}如果奇跡指向這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.93,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拭去盈眶的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.48,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}向前大步前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:31.32,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}解放我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:37.03,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}在如此的煉獄中會迷失前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:42.12,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:50.13,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}化為一道烈焰逝向彼方 這渾身的炙熱不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:57.38,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:16.18,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.11,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:33.79,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:42.71,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:51.26,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:02.19,ED_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:16.18,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人的孤獨 一時間的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:24.11,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你為我帶來的瑰寶 一樣樣都令人愛不釋手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:33.79,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕兩人之間的距離觸手可及 可無形之壁註定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:42.71,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心宛如明月 陰晴圓缺不斷變幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:51.26,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,約定依舊無法實現 眼淚仍然不願乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:02.19,ED_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只能把你給的瑰寶 緊擁懷中驀然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？夕..夕夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有點胖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！不可以看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法移開視線！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊..這是在夕子學姐的記憶之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂..難不成..！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 等一下 夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪之十 喪失少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個景色 60年前的記憶..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夕子學姐腦海中的..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是夕子學姐所丟棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保留在影夕子腦海中的記憶..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我實在是無能為力..看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起！夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸..胸部的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 夕子學姐的感覺也直接傳達給了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.51,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒 內向 害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成這個人就是夕子學姐的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是霧江同學的..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳又要去那孩子那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為昨天小淺也沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想多幫她做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果連姐姐也染上瘟疫的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是普通的感冒而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夫也說沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不該冒著危險去接近她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果為了那孩子 姐姐萬一發生了什麼不測..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳還要說這種話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在村子正經歷一段很艱難的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不大家互相幫一把的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我又不是孩子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子小姐她..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿她沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連夕子學姐雙唇的感觸都..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小..小指頭撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛..妳才是振作一點啦 夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近以前是礦山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是出產銅礦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後再給你東西吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中林先生家裏..大家都去世了啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是詛咒石上記載的那場瘟疫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子裏死了好多人 然後夕子學姐成了人柱的那場..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是安靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 小淺 今天感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶了早餐來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我馬上就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊 這個是罐裝的魚肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通的罐頭魚的味道..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 在這個時代裏罐頭很難得吃到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經吃飽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 吃一顆糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在一起的話 夕子姐姐也會染上瘟疫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夫也說了小淺得的不是瘟疫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人..夕子姐姐這個大騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽奶奶還有姐姐..大家都..大家都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然大家真的都很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小淺會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上也會因瘟疫而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！夕子姐姐也會得瘟疫的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果夕子姐姐死掉的話 我就..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 這個送給小淺做禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的時候 就把這個當成是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看 是一對的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人的話心裏怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺跟霧江同學好像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我們一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有和別人說過話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 總覺得大人們很嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大家心裏都不安地不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大家一定在想解決的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事到底會持續到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我雖然不知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不可以失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連希望都失去的話 那一切就結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是村長他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是要去學園嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是去討論今後的對策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們也應該去聽一聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我適可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 村子就全沒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說 我們也束手無策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中林一家子真的很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一個人都沒剩下..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把家具衣服全拿去燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榻榻米和衣櫃全都要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣已經是第幾家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全家死於瘟疫的話這已經是第十三家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有超過一半的人家 家裏都有一兩個人得病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也..活不長了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 就坐等著所有人一起完蛋嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是詛咒啊！絕對是詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你說是啥子詛咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在神社的遺跡上建了這學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你說那是神社的遺跡..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那裡因為空襲已經被燒得什麼都不剩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可也不能改變那裡曾經是神社的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有好好的驅邪消災過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是沒驅夠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沒埋上人柱就在神社遺跡上建造學園而產生的詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該供奉的東西不供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自說自話的蓋上了其他的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明老爺發怒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可就算你們這麼說 可現在也於事無補了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也只能趁現在把人柱補上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校的下面還留著祀堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開個洞馬上就能進去祭拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣做能平息神明老爺的憤怒的話就好..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可要埋的話埋誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這也沒什麼可以隨便埋的死囚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算埋了罪人和馬上要死的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明的憤怒也不會平息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,純潔年輕的生命作為活祭品才是最適合的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..小孩子是村子的寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且人身御供的人選要是讓村裏人知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都死了這麼多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再多不見一個人 也沒有人會擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他當成是因瘟疫而死的話 應該就不會有人察覺吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要選誰當人身御供呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選出一個紅人 把這個抉擇交給他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫作銅人讀作紅人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是銅礦山之神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用抽簽在村民裏選出一個紅人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而紅人所指的那個孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要被當作人柱埋在神社的遺跡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈異調查部的部室？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到哪裡去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是墻壁上沒有開孔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 不要出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他給逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被聽到了嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒聽到的話就不會逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 祀堂好像就在這附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別讓他給溜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這種事..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗茶淡飯多有見諒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去泡茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣..那拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎 夕子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我也跟妳們住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉色 好很多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是普通的感冒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人說要把小孩子當做人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不忍心放任小淺一個人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才把她叫來一起住嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人們好像都忙不過來了 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家的空房間也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把熱茶喝下去暖暖身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在體力正弱的時候要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的得瘟疫的話就不得了了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又全看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我可以一起進來洗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可..不不不不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人會很不安嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 那些人..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都什麼年代了還用人柱..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事不會被允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是地上汽車跑天上飛機飛的科學時代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種迷信能救得了誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須做點什麼來阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 如果做那種事讓姐姐卷入什麼危險的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒想過只讓自己得救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是姐姐妳 只有這點不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請珍重自己一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別小看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這個正需要大家互相扶持的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能自己一個人逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子小姐 是在為夕子學姐而擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的月亮..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐原來..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這麼一位感情豐富的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個普通的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.16,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經叫醫生以後來這邊幫妳看病了 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 東西都亂丟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果感冒又反復了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子 小淺呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在客廳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺到什麼時候還在客廳裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在我去洗澡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後就沒看見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我馬上就回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要補一補嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦 衣服破成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:14:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..置物小屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你們得逞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小淺啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史已經證明了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們..在幹什麼啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小..淺？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人大人叫出了名字啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人大人叫出了名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人大人指出了活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人大人選出了活祭品..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人大人選定了人柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人柱..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人柱..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳骨折了..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分..太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能治得好人的病啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有人得救呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺不用當人柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我成為人柱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淺和紫子就不會有事..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有事..太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣..就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..祀堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以勉強自己動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕啊 好怕會死掉..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再動了 夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的腳..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來..我好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腳斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫大夫來 來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我從這裡放出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都肯做 什麼都會聽你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們聽得見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我出去..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼..我做錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼！為什麼！為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼..好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷..好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子..好餓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼..我明明沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什麼都..沒有做錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰決定我是人柱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅人..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為那個孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明待她這麼溫柔..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全因為那孩子叫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對..不是那孩子的錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子..我好恨那孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子..難不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼能那麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那孩子的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..好難受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以..不可以恨小淺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不對..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯的不是我..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是別的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會..含恨..而死...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 恨的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恨..好恨..好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨把我當成人柱妄圖自己茍活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨殺死我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恨..好恨..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恨..好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是影夕子的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是..夕子學姐的怪談的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我離棄掉的妳..我好恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不見的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸不到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..你..
